dtm = rast("D:/Remote Sensing/AGB_project/Samlan_LASfiles/dtm1m.tif")
print(dtm)
## class       : SpatRaster 
## dimensions  : 4491, 5576, 1  (nrow, ncol, nlyr)
## resolution  : 1, 1  (x, y)
## extent      : 709298, 714874, 1593343, 1597834  (xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax)

## source      : dtm1m.tif 
## name        :       Z 
## min value   :   6.584

plot(dtm,main="DTM")

dtm_prod <- terra::terrain(dtm, v = c("slope", "aspect"), unit = "radians")
## 
|---------|---------|---------|---------|
=========================================
                                          
dtm_hillshade <- terra::shade(slope = dtm_prod$slope, aspect = dtm_prod$aspect)
plot(dtm_hillshade, col = gray(0:50/50), legend = FALSE)
